Name: django-hotsauce
Version: 0.9.8
Summary: Scalable and heterogeneous web toolkit sitting on top of Django and others
Home-page: https://www.isotopesoftware.ca/software/django-hotsauce/
Author: Etienne Robillard
Author-email: tkadm30@yandex.com
License: Apache License Version 2
Description: The Django-hotsauce toolkit is a experimental Python web framework based on WSGI 1.0 and Django 1.0.
        == Features ==
        * Native Schevo ORM and ZODB storage backend * High-performance PyPy (JIT) and Python 3.7 support on top of WSGI 1.0 * Enhanced nginx and uWSGI support * Generic authorization and authentication support (oauthlib, libauthkit) * Experimental gevent support * Commercial licenses available * etc...
Keywords: django-hotsauce uwsgi zodb libschevo libauthkit django
